						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Rājarāja III. Year 9: A.D. 1225.</hi></p>						

						<p>Built in at the beginning. Seems to refer an old grant of 1200 <hi rend="italic">kuḻis</hi> of land as <hi rend="italic">dēvadāṉa</hi> in Chintāmaṇipuram to the temple of Tiruvallidāyamuḍaiya Nāyaṉār by Nāḍāḻvāṉ of Chūriyaṉ Paiyyūr. These lands were now regranted by Saḷukki Nārāṇan Yādavarāyan.</p>						

