<p>
<lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> vanac cakkaravattikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> Irācarācatevaṟku yāṇṭu 9 vatu ceyaṅkoṇṭacoḻa maṇ
<lb n="2" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ppuḻaṟ koṭṭamāṉa vikkiracoḻa vaḷanāṭṭu Ampattūr nāṭṭu tiruvallitāyattil piṟi
<lb n="3" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> natil cintāmaṇipuram tiruvallitāyamuṭaiya nāyaṉāṟku cūriyaṉpaiyūr nāṭāḻvāṉ Acaṅkā
<lb n="4"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ṉ Ivvūril meviya pūntoṭṭam Iraṇṭum maṉai Iraṇṭum Uṭpaṭṭa kuḻi Āyirattirunūṟu 
<lb n="5"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ttevaṟkut tevatāṉamāka Oṉpatāvatu mutal cantirātittavarai cellakkaṭavatāka vi
<lb n="6" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> vaṉ viṭṭapaṭiye Innāyanāṟku cāḷukki nāraṇan yātavarāyaneṉ viṭṭeṉ
</p>

